docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:3:End-to-end reference for deploying the VFIDE contract suite to any network.
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:9:Before running any deploy script, ensure:
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:25:npx hardhat run scripts/deploy-full.ts --network baseSepolia
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:29:After this script completes, **save every deployed address** — addresses are persisted to `.deployments/<network>.json` automatically (resume-from-crash supported), and you will need them as env vars before running any subsequent script.
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:31:> **⚠️ 48-hour timelock:** All module setter calls made by `deploy-full.ts` are timelocked.
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:48:Run only the phases that are needed for the target deployment tier:
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:52:npx hardhat run scripts/future/deploy-phase2.ts --network baseSepolia
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:53:npx hardhat run scripts/future/deploy-phase3.ts --network baseSepolia
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:54:npx hardhat run scripts/future/deploy-phase4.ts --network baseSepolia
docs/DEPLOYMENT.md:55:npx hardhat run scripts/future/deploy-phase5.ts --network baseSepolia
