docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:10:| **phase-1** | `scripts/deploy-phase1.ts` | Access control, token, governance via factory deployers |
docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:11:| **phase-3** | `scripts/future/deploy-phase3.ts` | Bridge and peripherals via factory deployers |
docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:12:| **factory** | Deployed by Phase1/Phase3 factory contracts | Sub-deployed on-chain |
docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:13:| **deploy-wizard** | `scripts/deploy-wizard.sh` | Interactive wrapper around deploy-solo |
docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:14:| **manual** | Owner calls after core deploy | Wired by OwnerControlPanel or direct calls |
docs/DEPLOYMENT_MANIFEST.md:15:| **deferred** | Not yet needed | Will be deployed when feature is activated |
